\n<Reveler><wrap>Ahhh ehhh! Who's tha' makin' all the noise?
\n<Esther><Wrap>The King... Has he been through here?
\n<Reveler><wrap>The King? *hic* You think a King be here?! Yous *hic* a dense one, ain'ta.
\n<Reveler><wrap>What's wit tha *hic* gettup? You some kind o' humunc, humus, humanculups... *hic* you know what I mean...
\n<Reveler><wrap>What's tha song you *hic* were singing? Ne'er heard it before...
\n<Galathan><Wrap>\c[1]North Caembria\c[0] isn't far. We should restock in town before heading on to the \c[1]Eoten Mountain Pass\c[0] to the \c[1]North\c[0]..

\n<Villager><Wrap>Something attacked a merchant \c[1]north\c[0] of here, \c[1]near the coast\c[0]. Whatever it was, it was vicious! Only one person made it back here safely, but succumbed to their wounds.
\n<Caembrian Guard><Wrap>Captain! Nobody saw what happened last night. Some people say it was a drunken brawl, but I never seen a drunken brawl end with someone's guts hanging out like that...

\n<Villager><Wrap>I found some old ruins to the \c[1]South-East\c[0]. I couldn't get close, though, there were a lot of creatures around them! I even heard there were more ruins on the other side of the \c[1]Eoten Mountain Pass\c[0].
